#

Wild Mushroom Risotto with Truffle Oil and Grilled Asparagus

$25
650 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

MushroomsDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeNut-Free

Tags:

ItalianGourmetComfort Food

Description

A rich and creamy risotto featuring earthy wild mushrooms and a touch of luxurious truffle oil, paired with perfectly grilled asparagus.

Ingredients

  • Arborio rice: 1 cup
  • Wild mushrooms (e.g., shiitake, oyster, cremini): 2 cups
  • Vegetable stock: 4 cups
  • White wine: 1/2 cup
  • Shallots: 2, finely chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Butter: 3 tablespoons
  • Truffle oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Asparagus: 1 bunch
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
